data.description: This is it! Roomy 3 bedroom, 2 bath house in Creekside Manor subdivision, with no HOA fees. Open kitchen with an island. Walk in closets, with plenty of storage. New roof on sun room. Fenced back yard. Come take a look! Back on the market after Buyer's financing fell through, again.
